\begin{abstract}
In this paper, we study rotational surfaces of elliptic, hyperbolic and
parabolic types with pointwise 1-type Gauss map in four dimensional pseudo
Euclidean space  $\mathbb{E}_{2}^{4}$\ and give some characterizations for these rotational surfaces with pointwise 1-type Gauss map.
\end{abstract}

\begin{quote}\small
{\it{Key words}:Pseudo- Euclidean space, Rotational Surfaces of elliptic,
hyperbolic or parabolic type, Gauss map, Pointwise 1-Type Gauss map.}
\end{quote}
